MARKDOWN CODE FOR DATA SOURCE LINKS AND FRED CODES

| **Variable** | **Description** | **Source** |
|--------------|-----------------|------------|
| **R** | Binary recession indicator series | National Bureau of Economic Research — https://www.nber.org/cycles/cyclesmain.html and Federal Reserve Economic Data (FRED): https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/USRECPQ#0 |
| **CGDP** | Credit-to-GDP ratio (total credit to private non-financial sector, % GDP) | Federal Reserve Economic Data of the Federal Reserve Bank of St. Louis web: https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/QUSPAM770A |
| **CPIR** | Consumer price index ratio | Consumer Price Index for All Urban Consumers (CPIAUCSL), monthly series from the Federal Reserve Bank of St. Louis (FRED), aggregated to quarterly frequency and converted to quarterly inflation rates. | inflation_q |
| **MA** | Purchasing Managers Index — Manufacturing | Institute for Supply Management (ISM) |
| **INVR** | Gross fixed capital formation growth rate (nonfinancial corporate business; gross fixed capital formation with equity REIT residential structures) | Federal Reserve Economic Data of the Federal Reserve Bank of St. Louis |
| **HP** | Residential house prices index (new 1-family houses, per dwelling) | Bank of International Settlements (FRED hosts the BIS data. Series: "Real Residential Property Prices for United States")|  
| **IR** | Interest rate (real) | Federal Reserve Economic Data of the Federal Reserve Bank of St. Louis |  
| **ROP** | Profit rate (nonfinancial corporations’ sector) | Federal Reserve Economic Data of the Federal Reserve Bank of St. Louis |  
| **IROR** | Incremental rate of profit per unit of investment | Authors’ calculations |  
| **LSOI** | Labour’s share of income (nonfarm business sector) | Federal Reserve Economic Data of the Federal Reserve Bank of St. Louis |  
| **TOBQ** | Tobin’s Q | YCharts — https://ycharts.com/indicators/tobins_q | 
| **RGDP** | Real gross domestic product growth | Federal Reserve Economic Data of the Federal Reserve Bank of St. Louis |  

**Note:** The sample period for all variables is 1963Q1–2018Q2, except for Tobin’s Q, where data were available for 1963Q1–2017Q4.

**Manufacturing PMI (MA):**

- Source: Institute for Supply Management (ISM).

- This data is NOT available on FRED (it is proprietary).

**Tobin's Q (TOBQ):**

- Source: YCharts.

- This data is NOT available on FRED

### FRED Source Series IDs

| Variable | Description | FRED Series ID | FRED Website or other |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **R** | NBER Recession Indicator | `USRECQ` | FRED - https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/USRECQ |
| **CGDP** | Credit-to-GDP Ratio | `QUSPAM770A` | FRED - https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/QUSPAM770A|
| **CPIR** | Consumer Price Index | `CPIAUCSL` | FRED - https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/CPIAUCSL|
| **MA** | Purchasing Managers Index — Manufacturing | N/A | Institute for Supply Management (ISM) |
| **INVR** | Gross Fixed Capital Formation | `B009RC1Q027SBEA` | FRED - https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/B009RC1Q027SBEA |
| **HP** | House Prices | `QUSR628BIS` |FRED - https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/QUSR628BIS|
| **IR** | Interest Rate (Real) | `TB3MS` (Nominal) - `CPIAUCSL` (inflation) |FRED - CPIAUCSL - https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/CPIAUCSL TB3MS - https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/TB3MS|
| **ROP** | Profit Rate (Net Operating Surplus) | `A445RC1Q027SBEA` | FRED - https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/A445RC1Q027SBEA|
| **LSOI** | Labour's Share of Income | `PRS85006173` | FRED - https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/PRS85006173|
| **TOBQ** | Tobin’s Q | N/A | YCharts — https://ycharts.com/indicators/tobins_q | 
| **RGDP** | Real GDP Growth | `GDPC1` | FRED - https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/GDPC1|


